    <p>{`After selecting a Permission Group, you can choose what level of access to grant the token. Most groups offer `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Edit`}</inlineCode>{` or `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Read`}</inlineCode>{` options. `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Edit`}</inlineCode>{` is full `}<em parentName="p">{`CRUDL`}</em>{` (`}<em parentName="p">{`create`}</em>{`, `}<em parentName="p">{`read`}</em>{`, `}<em parentName="p">{`update`}</em>{`, `}<em parentName="p">{`delete`}</em>{`, `}<em parentName="p">{`list`}</em>{`) access, while `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Read`}</inlineCode>{` is just the `}<em parentName="p">{`read`}</em>{` permission and `}<em parentName="p">{`list`}</em>{` where appropriate.`}</p>
